    <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NEO Mission</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
        .choices label { display: block; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 1.2em; }
        .intel { background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Mission: Hazard Assessment</h1>
    <p>Intel analysis is required. Of the following Near-Earth Objects approaching today, which one will have the closest flyby (smallest miss distance)?</p>
    
    <div class="intel">
        <strong>Intel Tip:</strong> Use the <a href="/neo" target="_blank">NEO Tracker</a> to analyze the miss distances.
    </div>

    <form action="/submit-neo-mission" method="POST" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="choices">
            <% choices.forEach(choice => { %>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="userAnswer" value="<%= choice %>" required>
                    <%= choice %>
                </label>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
        
        <input type="hidden" name="correctAnswer" value="<%= correctAnswer %>">
        <button type="submit" style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px;">Submit Assessment</button>
    </form>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><a href="/dashboard">Return to Dashboard</a></p>

</body>
</html>